Sub tickerChecker()

    For Each ws In Worksheets
          
        Dim ticker As String
        
        Dim openingPrice As Double
        openingPrice = 0
        
        Dim closePrice As Double
        closePrice = 0
        
        Dim yearlyChange As Double
    
        Dim percentageChange As Double
    
        Dim totalStockVolume As Double
        totalStockVolume = 0
    
        Dim summaryTableRow As Long
        summaryTableRow = 2
        
        Dim lastRow As Long
        lastRow = ws.Cells(ws.Rows.Count, 1).End(xlUp).Row
        
        Dim greatestIncrease As Double
        Dim greatestDecrease As Double
        Dim greatestTotalVolumn As Double
        
        ws.Range("I1,P1").Value = "Ticker"
        ws.Range("J1").Value = "Yearly Change"
        ws.Range("K1").Value = "Percentage Change"
        ws.Range("L1").Value = "Total Stock Volume"
        ws.Range("O2").Value = "Greatest % Increase"
        ws.Range("O3").Value = "Greatest % Decrease"
        ws.Range("O4").Value = "Greatest Total Volumn"
        ws.Range("Q1").Value = "Value"

For j = 2 To lastRow
                
        
                If ws.Cells(j + 1, 1).Value <> ws.Cells(j, 1).Value Then
                    ticker = ws.Cells(j, 1).Value
                    totalStockVolume = totalStockVolume + ws.Cells(j, 7).Value
                    closePrice = ws.Cells(j, 6).Value
                    openingPrice = ws.Cells(j - 250, 3).Value
                    yearlyChange = closePrice - openingPrice
                    percentageChange = (yearlyChange / openingPrice)
                    ws.Range("I" & summaryTableRow).Value = ticker
                    ws.Range("J" & summaryTableRow).Value = yearlyChange
                    ws.Range("K" & summaryTableRow).Value = percentageChange
                    ws.Range("L" & summaryTableRow).Value = totalStockVolume
                    totalStockVolume = 0
                    If yearlyChange < 0 Then
                        ws.Range("J" & summaryTableRow).Interior.ColorIndex = 3
                    Else
                        ws.Range("J" & summaryTableRow).Interior.ColorIndex = 4
                    End If
                    summaryTableRow = summaryTableRow + 1
                    ws.Columns("K").NumberFormat = "0.00%"
                                    
                                        
                Else
                    totalStockVolume = totalStockVolume + ws.Cells(j, 7).Value
                End If
                
                greatestIncrease = Application.WorksheetFunction.Max(ws.Range("K:K"))
                ws.Range("Q2").Value = greatestIncrease
                                          
                greatestDecrease = Application.WorksheetFunction.Min(ws.Range("K:K"))
                ws.Range("Q3").Value = greatestDecrease
                ws.Range("Q2,Q3").NumberFormat = "0.00%"
                                
                greatestTotalVolumn = Application.WorksheetFunction.Max(ws.Range("L:L"))
                ws.Range("Q4").Value = greatestTotalVolumn
                    
                    If ws.Cells(j, 11).Value = greatestIncrease Then
                        ws.Range("P2").Value = ws.Cells(j, 9).Value
                    End If
                    
                    If ws.Cells(j, 11).Value = greatestDecrease Then
                        ws.Range("P3").Value = ws.Cells(j, 9).Value
                    End If
                    
                    If ws.Cells(j, 12).Value = greatestTotalVolumn Then
                        ws.Range("P4").Value = ws.Cells(j, 9).Value
                    End If
